        </p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300 font-normal">
          <strong>How to perform:</strong> Hold the towel taut in front of you at chest height. Keeping your arms straight and the towel tight, slowly rotate your upper body to one side while keeping your hips facing forward. Turn your head to look in the same direction. Hold for 10 seconds, then return to center and repeat on the other side. Do 5-8 repetitions per side.
        </p>

